      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks that's a relief. i was worried i might need to go back to the clinic but i really don't want to deal with the wait times and the cost of another appointment. if i use the antibiotic cream twice a day and keep doing the warm compresses, do you think it'll clear up on its own in a couple of days? i'm pretty sure the cream i have is fine to use.",
